    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Defroster Fans (Optional)</title>
        <para>The defroster fans are optional equipment and when specified are mounted on the front header assembly.
            More than one fan may be specified. The fans are adjustable horizontally and vertically. To remove the
            defroster fan:
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate the 3 mounting base screws (
                <hotlnk document="s47004_63.xml" xrefid="f4700487">Fig. 87, Item 1</hotlnk>), loosen and remove.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Disconnect the fan harness plug. Remove the defroster fan.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
